* (Australian Centre for Egyptology Studies: 2) Naguib Kanawati, with a Chapter by Ann McFarlane, ''Akhmim in the Old Kingdom, Part I: Chronology and Administration", (Sydney, 1992). {{ISBN|0-85668-603-4}}.

