awyet el'Aryan]] || [[Unfinished Northern Pyramid of Zawyet el'Aryan]] || [[File:Vue3-grande-excavation.jpg|80x80px]] |- | align="center" | '''XIV''' || Zawyet el'Aryan || [[Layer Pyramid]] || [[File:Khaba_pyramid_at_Zawyet_el'Aryan.jpg|80x80px]] |- style="background-color: #ffe39b; color: #773300 " | colspan="4" height="5" | |- bgcolor="#EEEEEE" | align="center" | '''XV''' || [[Abu Gorab]] || Sun temple of Nyuserre Ini || [[File:Solar Temple of Niuserre.jpg|80x80px]] |- style="background-color: #ffe39b; color: #773300 " | colspan="4" height="5" | |- bgcolor="#EEEEEE" | align="center" | '''XVI''' || [[Abusir]] || Unidentified brick pyramid || |- bgcolor="#EEEEEE" | align="center" | '''XVII''' || Abusir || [[Sun temple of Userkaf]] || |- | align="center" | '''XVIII''' || Abusir || [[Pyramid of Sahure]] || [[File:Abousir Sahoure 01.jpg|80x80px]] |- bgcolor="#EEEEEE" | align="center" | '''XIX''' || Abusir || Mastaba of vizier [[Ptahshepses]] || [[File:Mastaba de Ptahchepsès.JPG|80x80px]] |- | align="center" | '''XX''' || Abusir || [[Pyramid of Nyuserre]] || [[File:Pyramid of Niuserre.jpg|80x80px]] |- | align="center" | '''XXI''' || Abusir || [[Pyramid of Neferirkare]] || [[File:Neferirkare.jpg|80x80px]] |- bgcolor="#EEEEEE" | align="center" | '''XXII''' || Abusir || Small satellite pyramid || |- bgcolor="#EEEEEE" | align="center" | '''XXIII''' || Abusir || Small satellite pyramid || |- | align="center" | '''XXIV''' || Abusir || Pyramid ''[[Lepsius XXIV]]'', queen of Nyuserre Ini || [[File:Lepsius-XXIV pyramid.jpg|80x80px]] |- | align="center" | '''XXV''' || Abusir || [[Double Pyramid]], queen of Nyuserre Ini or Neferefre, could be a double mastaba || [[File:Lepsius-XXV pyramid.jpg|80x80px]] |- | align="center" | '''XXVI''' || Abusir || [[Pyramid of Neferefre]] || [[File:Pyramid of Neferefre, Abusir, 1970ies.jpg|80x80px]] |- bgcolor="#EEEEEE" | align="center" | '''XXVII''' || Abusir || Completely destroyed, only an outline is visible || |- bgcolor="#EEEEEE" | align="cen