t || [[Pyramid of Senusret I]] || [[File:Licht-senwsPyramids 01.jpg|80x80px]] |- bgcolor="#EEEEEE" | align="center" | '''LXII''' || El-Lisht || Mastaba, unknown owner || |- bgcolor="#EEEEEE" | align="center" | '''LXIII''' || El-Lisht ||Mastaba of [[Senewosret-Ankh]]{{sfn|Arnold|2008|pp=13–24|loc=pls. 2–7, 9–25, pls. 62–92, pl. 129–133.}}|| |- bgcolor="#EEEEEE" | align="center" | '''LXIV''' || El-Lisht ||Mastaba, possibly belonging to a private individual named Senusret{{sfn|Arnold|2008|pp=24–26|loc=pls. 26–31, pls. 62–92, pl. 129–133}}|| |- style="background-color: #ffe39b; color: #773300 " | colspan="4" height="5" | |- | align="center" | '''LXV''' || [[Meidum]] || [[Meidum#Pyramid|Pyramid of Meidum]] || [[Image:Meidoum pyramide 006.JPG|80x80px]] |- style="background-color: #ffe39b; color: #773300 " | colspan="4" height="5" | |- | align="center" | '''LXVI''' || [[El-Lahun]] || [[Pyramid of Senusret II]] || [[File:Pyramid at Lahun.jpg|80x80px]] |- style="background-color: #ffe39b; color: #773300 " | colspan="4" height="5" | |- | align="center" | '''LXVII''' || [[Hawara]] || [[Pyramid of Hawara]], of Amenemhat III. Situated north of "The Labyrinth" || [[File:Hawara.jpg|80x80px]] |} </center>
