er-blog.com/2016/12/izirtu-tapeh-qalaychi-near-bukan-in-iran.html|title=Izirtu: Tapeh Qalaychi near Bukan in Iran - Bronze age towns|last=Gastineau|first=Bob|work=Bronze age towns|access-date=2018-04-03|language=en-US}}</ref> * [[Rabat Tepe]] * [[Paishiyauvada]] * [[Temukan]] * Arjan * [[Darab|Darabgard]] * [[Hafshejan]] * [[Bandar Siraf]] * [[Nishapur]] * [[Tus, Iran|Tus]](Susia) * [[Gundeshapur]] * [[Tabriz]] * [[Yazd]] * [[Kangavar]] * [[Shahdad]] * [[Qasr-e Shirin]] * [[Meybod]] * Ashraf Tepe * [[Marlik]] * [[Amlash culture|Amlash]] * ''Gohar Tepe''<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.payvand.com/news/11/dec/1288.html|title=Photos: Gohar Tepe Historical Site|website=www.payvand.com|access-date=2018-04-03}}</ref> * Kelar Tepe * [[Chogha Bonut]] * [[Ganj Dareh]] * Tepe Sarab<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://is.muni.cz/el/1421/jaro2012/PAPVA_03/um/TepeSarab-TEHRAN.pdf|title=FROM SARAB TO ALI KOSH TO TULA’I The Iranian Neolithic in the 1960s|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref> * Tepe Giyan<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/giyan-tepe|title=GIYAN TEPE – Encyclopaedia Iranica|last=electricpulp.com|website=www.iranicaonline.org|language=en|access-date=2018-04-03}}</ref> * Tepe Guran<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.peeters-leuven.be/boekoverz.asp?nr=9406|title=Excavations at Tepe Guran|website=www.peeters-leuven.be|access-date=2018-04-03}}</ref> * [[Ali Kosh]] * Tepe Asiab * Tepe Haftvan<ref>{{Cite book|title=The Routledge Handbook of the Peoples and Places of Ancient Western Asia|last=|first=|publisher=|year=|isbn=|location=|pages=274}}</ref> * Tepe Ghabrestan Buin Zahra * [[Ellipi]] * Tal-i-Iblis * [[Arisman]] * [[Abyaneh]] * [[Geoy Tepe]] * [[Bābā Jān Tepe|Baba Jan Tepe]] * [[Shah Tepe]] * [[Hajji Firuz Tepe]] * [[Kul Tepe Jolfa|Kul Tepe]] * [[Shir Ashian Tepe]] * [[Tureng Tepe]] * [[Yarim Tepe (Iran)|Yarim Tepe]] * [[Kukherd]] * Vahrkana ([[Gorgan]]) * Narezzash ([[Neyriz]]) * Zranka ([[Dahan-e Gholaman]]) *